INFO 06-17 10:20:52 logger.py:37] Received request cmpl-826c58ee6d174c2b864b45e376157657-0: prompt: 'Assistant: Some of the portals that are required in tribal districts of India and may not be present are:\n\n1. Tribal welfare portal: A portal that provides information and services related to the welfare of tribal communities, such as education, health, employment, and social security schemes. This portal can help to bridge the gap between the government and tribal communities and improve the implementation of tribal welfare schemes.\n2. Forest and wildlife portal: A portal that provides information and services related to forest and wildlife management, such as forest conservation, wildlife protection, and eco-tourism. This portal can help to create awareness among the local population about the importance of forest and wildlife conservation and encourage them to participate in conservation efforts.\n3. Agriculture and horticulture portal: A portal that provides information and services related to agriculture and horticulture, such as crop production, marketing, and value addition. This portal can help to improve the livelihoods of farmers and promote sustainable agriculture practices in the tribal areas.\n4. Tourism portal: A portal that promotes the tourist destinations and cultural heritage of the tribal districts. This portal can help to create job opportunities in the tourism sector and generate income for the local communities.\n5. Disaster management portal: A portal that provides information and services related to disaster management, such as early warning systems, emergency response, and relief and rehabilitation measures. This portal can help to reduce the vulnerability of the tribal communities to natural disasters and improve their preparedness to deal with emergencies.\n6. Education portal: A portal that provides information and services related to education, such as scholarships, vocational training, and career guidance. This portal can help to improve the quality of education in the tribal areas and promote skill development among the local youth.\n\nThe implementation of these portals can help to address the specific needs and challenges of the tribal districts and improve the delivery of services to the citizens.\nUser: design a proposal to provide these portal\nAssistant:', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=-1, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=8, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None), prompt_token_ids: [71703, 25, 4329, 315, 279, 75463, 429, 525, 2567, 304, 39389, 26438, 315, 6747, 323, 1231, 537, 387, 3042, 525, 1447, 16, 13, 90112, 22634, 23132, 25, 362, 23132, 429, 5707, 1995, 323, 3516, 5435, 311, 279, 22634, 315, 39389, 10744, 11, 1741, 438, 6731, 11, 2820, 11, 14402, 11, 323, 3590, 4763, 30856, 13, 1096, 23132, 646, 1492, 311, 14164, 279, 12929, 1948, 279, 3033, 323, 39389, 10744, 323, 7269, 279, 8129, 315, 39389, 22634, 30856, 624, 17, 13, 19988, 323, 29305, 23132, 25, 362, 23132, 429, 5707, 1995, 323, 3516, 5435, 311, 13638, 323, 29305, 6240, 11, 1741, 438, 13638, 28611, 11, 29305, 9135, 11, 323, 41588, 2385, 413, 2142, 13, 1096, 23132, 646, 1492, 311, 1855, 17526, 4221, 279, 2205, 7042, 911, 279, 12650, 315, 13638, 323, 29305, 28611, 323, 14907, 1105, 311, 15759, 304, 28611, 8869, 624, 18, 13, 36863, 323, 305, 371, 92728, 23132, 25, 362, 23132, 429, 5707, 1995, 323, 3516, 5435, 311, 28929, 323, 305, 371, 92728, 11, 1741, 438, 19097, 5670, 11, 8493, 11, 323, 897, 5256, 13, 1096, 23132, 646, 1492, 311, 7269, 279, 63651, 82, 315, 20336, 323, 11926, 21803, 28929, 12378, 304, 279, 39389, 5671, 624, 19, 13, 51552, 23132, 25, 362, 23132, 429, 38890, 279, 29970, 33105, 323, 12752, 27848, 315, 2