ons about future campaigns.\nUser: Write a tl;dr of the campaigns concept\nAssistant: "Campaigns" is a feature in a web application that allows users to create targeted marketing or promotion efforts using NFC technology. When an NFC object associated with a campaign is scanned, the end-user is redirected to a specific forward URL. Users can configure a set of NFC objects to be included in the campaign by specifying a list of tags and can choose to run the campaign within a specific timeframe or indefinitely. The results of the campaign, including the number of scanned objects and the locations of the scans, can be visualized in a dashboard. The dashboard can be used to monitor the progress of ongoing campaigns or review the results of completed campaigns.\nUser: Please write a shorter summary\nAssistant:', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=-1, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=8, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None), prompt_token_ids: [1474, 25, 9645, 1196, 7343, 429, 7512, 419, 7286, 304, 7716, 198, 71703, 25, 5692, 525, 1045, 1196, 7343, 429, 7512, 279, 4796, 4565, 304, 7716, 1447, 2121, 264, 8493, 6645, 11, 358, 1366, 311, 1855, 264, 4796, 311, 11926, 264, 501, 1985, 13, 358, 1366, 311, 3293, 264, 1874, 315, 47205, 6171, 429, 525, 5815, 448, 279, 1985, 323, 2924, 1105, 304, 279, 4796, 13, 358, 1083, 1366, 311, 13837, 264, 4637, 5548, 429, 3847, 686, 387, 48928, 311, 979, 807, 8569, 458, 47205, 1633, 13, 358, 1366, 311, 387, 2952, 311, 738, 264, 69953, 369, 279, 4796, 323, 3754, 279, 3059, 304, 264, 26967, 773, 429, 358, 646, 1490, 1246, 1657, 1251, 525, 31788, 279, 4796, 323, 1380, 807, 525, 7407, 382, 2121, 264, 2613, 2562, 6372, 11, 358, 1366, 311, 