udience and receive real-time tips. Once a person tips, we keep their card on file to make it easy to tip.\n\nFitclass encourages our trainers to not have a paywall for their classes or to charge people for their classes. This will limit exposure. By doing classes for Free, it\'s like Twitch or Youtube live. You, in fact, become a health streamer. You can look at FitClass as a health Streaming Platform. Twitch is for gamers, Youtube live is for content creators, and fitclass.com is for health and wellness professionals to stream their classes live to a global audience and receive real-time tips.\n\nIf you\'re ready to take your health and wellness career to the next level, join Fitclass now and start reaching a global audience and earning money through tips. Sign up now and become a Fitclass trainer.\nUser: write me the copy for the "Get Fit at Home page"\nAssistant:', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=-1, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=8, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None), prompt_token_ids: [71703, 25, 10869, 12353, 25, 29890, 1040, 481, 20721, 35708, 57258, 481, 2126, 29890, 2411, 5379, 271, 12175, 7662, 25, 29890, 1040, 374, 279, 16724, 4108, 17042, 29533, 1380, 498, 646, 6997, 264, 6884, 8045, 315, 17042, 6846, 11, 1795, 697, 6930, 50091, 11, 323, 10091, 697, 536, 36769, 323, 40062, 448, 14219, 13, 16471, 601, 1431, 323, 633, 4946, 518, 2114, 2219, 43842, 25, 4108, 17042, 11, 17042, 6846, 11, 50091, 11, 25242, 11, 2114, 18813, 11, 1795, 50091, 11, 10091, 536, 36769, 11, 40062, 11, 633, 4946, 518, 2114, 271, 12223, 10869, 25, 2126, 29890, 2411, 5379, 448, 29890, 1040, 481, 20721, 35708, 57258, 271, 12223, 7662, 25, 32939, 264, 6884, 8045, 315, 17