udience and receive real-time tips. Once a person tips, we keep their card on file to make it easy to tip.\n\nFitclass encourages our trainers to not have a paywall for their classes or to charge people for their classes. This will limit exposure. By doing classes for Free, it\'s like Twitch or Youtube live. You, in fact, become a health streamer. You can look at FitClass as a health Streaming Platform. Twitch is for gamers, Youtube live is for content creators, and fitclass.com is for health and wellness professionals to stream their classes live to a global audience and receive real-time tips.\n\nIf you\'re ready to take your health and wellness career to the next level, join Fitclass now and start reaching a global audience and earning money through tips. Sign up now and become a Fitclass trainer.\nUser: write me the copy for the "Get Fit at Home page"\nAssistant: Welcome to the Get Fit at Home page, where you can discover the benefits of using Fitclass to workout from the comfort of your own home. With Fitclass, you can access a variety of fitness classes, follow your favorite trainers, and manage your class schedules and reservations with ease.\n\nOur platform is free for attendees to join and easy to use. You can browse through our fitness categories, classes, and trainers, and book free and paid classes. We offer a wide variety of classes such as Yoga, Pilates, Cardio Kickboxing, Spinning, Zumba, Body Pump, CrossFit, Bootcamp, Body Combat, Barre, Hot Yoga, TRX, Insanity, P90X, Hot Pilates, Tai Chi, Bikram Yoga, Rowing, Kettlebell, and HIIT.\n\nOne of the main benefits of using Fitclass is that you can workout from the comfort of your own home. You don\'t have to pay to belong to a gym or drive to a gym. It also removes the embarrassment and anxiety a person can sometimes have when they first join a gym, and they are out of shape, and everyone else is in shape. Working out at home, you can leave the webcam on or off. And for the disabled, obese, or elderly can even participate right from a chair, couch, bed, or rake rests without feeling like they don\'t belong in the class.\n\nFitclass also has a built-in tips system, where you can tip your trainer during the training session, just like Twitch or Youtube live. So, you can support your favorite trainers, and they can earn money while streaming their classes.\n\nIf you\'re ready to take your fitness journey to the next level, join Fitclass now and start getting fit at home. Sign up now and start your Fitclass journey.\nUser: Write me 10 FAQ\'s\nAssistant:', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=-1, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=8, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None), prompt_token_ids: [71703, 25, 10869, 12353, 25, 29890, 1040, 481, 20721, 35708, 57258, 481, 2126, 29890, 2411, 5379, 271, 12175, 7662, 25, 29890, 1040, 374, 279, 16724, 4108, 17042, 29533, 1380, 498, 646, 6997, 264, 6884, 8045, 315, 17042, 6846, 11, 1795, 697, 6930, 50091, 11, 323, 10091, 697, 536, 36769, 323, 40062, 448, 14219, 13, 16471, 601, 1431, 323, 633, 4946, 518, 2114, 2219, 43842, 25, 4108, 17042, 11, 17042, 6846, 11, 50091, 11, 25242, 11, 2114, 18813, 11, 1795, 50091, 11, 10091, 536, 36769, 11, 40062, 11, 633, 4946, 518, 2114, 271, 12223, 10869, 25, 2126, 29890, 2411, 5379, 448, 29890, 1040, 481, 20721, 35708, 57258, 271, 12223, 7662, 25, 32939, 264, 6884, 8045, 315, 17042, 6846, 11, 1795, 697, 6930, 50091, 11, 323, 10091, 697, 536, 36769, 323, 40062, 448, 14219, 13, 16471, 279, 29890, 1040, 3942, 1431, 323, 633, 4946, 518, 2114, 2219, 12223, 4654, 2918, 25, 29890, 1040, 481, 20721, 35708, 57258, 481, 2126, 29890, 2411, 5379, 271, 8078, 2704, 311, 990, 279, 1467, 323, 279, 12426, 315, 27